作者: 桃桃(flee)
题目: about the process
日期: Mon Feb 21 05:35:25 2000
1) at the noon of Monday, start deal with player complains,
if jury elected already, sentence cases according to jury's
options; otherwise, elect for new jury members. then wait for
next round.
2) jury do not have to present in the process, however, they
have to give option, which is saved in union_d.o
3) after all cases settled. it may take half hour at most ..
after finish, elect for new jury members, wait for next round.
4) from this Monday to next Thursday, player can add new complains
all players can view their reasons and suggestions. and all
players are able to give their own comments for the complains.
5) it is jury's responsiblity to read all reasons, suggestions
and comments from other players as well. but they can not make
their decision within this period.
6) after Thursday, no new complains will be accepted.
7) jury members can make decision anytime before next monday noon ..


